    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美联储应降低费率以帮助关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-to-help-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统表示，随着美国关税开始过渡到经济，美联储应降低利率。特朗普敦促美联储在关于真理社会的帖子中“做正确的事”。凯文·惠特拉（Kevin Whitelaw）在彭博电视台上报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-to-help-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 10:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债扩大了美联储的收益，因为市场赌注较低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/treasuries-extend-gains-from-fed-as-market-bets-on-lower-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国库在周三的联邦储备裁决上延长了收益，因为市场保证决策者仍在迈向较低利率的道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/treasuries-extend-gains-from-fed-as-market-bets-on-lower-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 09:51:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
